{"lemma":"شِمْراخُ","slug":"شِمْراخُ","root":"ش.م.ر.خ","root_slug":"ش-م-ر-خ","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-م-ر-خ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22983"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%90%D9%85%D9%92%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AE%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"alternative form of شُمْرُوخ (šumrūḵ)","tags":["alt-of","alternative"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʃim.raːx/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22983","headword_ar":"شِمْرَاخٌ","root":"$mrx","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$umoruwxN","text_ar":"شُمْرُوخٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fruit-"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stalk of the raceme of a palm-tree;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh;) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EivokaAl","text_ar":"عِثْكَال"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which are the dates;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, Msb;) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any one of the stalks that branch off from the main stem of the raceme, and on which hang the dates; each of these stalks comprising a number of dates, one below another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] pl. of both"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaAriyxu","text_ar":"شَمَارِيخُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei*oq","text_ar":"عِذْق"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kibaAsap","text_ar":"كِبَاسَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", [q. v.,] comprises the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaAriyx","text_ar":"شَمَارِيخ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei*oqN","text_ar":"عِذْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EivokaAl","text_ar":"عِثْكَال"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which are unripe dates,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grapes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) originally relating to a raceme of dates; but sometimes, to grapes: (L:) and the former word [or each] signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small bunch of grapes, growing apart, but attached to the lower portion of the stalk of a larger bunch."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$imoraAxN","text_ar":"شِمْرَاخٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"head of a mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a round, tall, slender head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"peak, of a mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) accord. to As, [the pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaAriyxu","text_ar":"شَمَارِيخُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heads of mountains:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or it signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upper,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uppermost, part"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"parts"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of a mountain; and in like manner, of trees. (Ham p. 786.) And (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upper,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uppermost, parts of clouds:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or [the pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaAriyxu","text_ar":"شَمَارِيخُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is metaphorically applied to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upper,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uppermost, parts"},{"kind":"text","text":"of clouds. (Ham ubi suprà.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A blaze upon the face of a horse, when it is narrow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and long,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and extending so as to cover the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part of the nose called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayo$uwm","text_ar":"خَيْشُوم"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but not reaching to the lip:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a blaze, upon the face of a horse, extending downwards on the nose."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gur~apN saAy^ilapN","text_ar":"غُرَّةٌ سَايِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"syl","text_ar":"سيل"},{"kind":"text","text":".] Accord. to J, The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"horse itself"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has such a blaze"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is also thus called; but this is a mistake: (K:) it seems that he meant to have said"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw $imoraAxK","text_ar":"ذُو شِمْرَاخٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but this, in a verse which he cites, is the name of a horse of Málik Ibn-'Owf En-Nadree, as is said in the K. (MF.) ―         -b4-  [The pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~amaAriyxu","text_ar":"الشَّمَارِيخُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also a name applied by the Arabs to (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The stars of Centaurus"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qanoTuwrus","text_ar":"قَنْطُورُس"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and Lepus"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~abuEu","text_ar":"السَّبُعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collectively."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kzw.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","L","TA"]}]}}